     <body>
     <div type="poem">
   <pb facs="9"/>
   <head>The Authours Petition.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>VAst Sea of Glory, who art blest</l>
      <l>With an Eternall Calme, rayse in my brest</l>
      <l>Tempests of Sorrow, stormes of sighes,</l>
      <l>Let waues of teares breake through myne eyes,</l>
      <l>That they may quench, ere life is done,</l>
      <l>The dreadfull wrath of thy deare Sonne.</l>
   </lg>
</div>
